    {
      "bookmarkId": "38793820_98_1021-1038",
      "chapterUid": 98,
      "range": "1021-1038",
      "markText": "资本生产过程的实质是生产剩余价值。",
      "totalCount": 637,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38793820&chapterUid=98&rangeStart=1021&rangeEnd=1038",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/64e325b0724ff25c64eeff7?chapterUid=98&rangeStart=1021&rangeEnd=1038"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38793820_127_16907-16951",
      "chapterUid": 127,
      "range": "16907-16951",
      "markText": "资本主义积累的历史趋势，就是资本主义必然灭亡，这是社会发展不以人的意志为转移的客观规律。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38793820&chapterUid=127&rangeStart=16907&rangeEnd=16951",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/64e325b0724ff25c64eeff7?chapterUid=127&rangeStart=16907&rangeEnd=16951"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38793820_96_1895-1922",
      "chapterUid": 96,
      "range": "1895-1922",
      "markText": "工业较发达国家的现状，就是工业较不发达国家未来的景象。",
      "totalCount": 602,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38793820&chapterUid=96&rangeStart=1895&rangeEnd=1922",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/64e325b0724ff25c64eeff7?chapterUid=96&rangeStart=1895&rangeEnd=1922"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38793820_100_4981-5057",
      "chapterUid": 100,
      "range": "4981-5057",
      "markText": "正是由于缝和织是两种不同质的劳动，才形成了上衣和麻布不同的使用价值；而正是因为这两种劳动质的区别被抽去，让它们成为同质的劳动，才形成了上衣和麻布的价值。",
      "totalCount": 602,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38793820&chapterUid=100&rangeStart=4981&rangeEnd=5057",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/64e325b0724ff25c64eeff7?chapterUid=100&rangeStart=4981&rangeEnd=5057"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38793820_96_2740-2855",
      "chapterUid": 96,
      "range": "2740-2855",
      "markText": "一个社会即使探索到了社会发展的客观规律（本书的最终目的就是要揭示现代社会经济运动的客观规律），也不能跳过更不能用法令来取消社会的自然发展阶段，即便它能缩短和减轻“分娩”的痛苦。",
      "totalCount": 588,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38793820&chapterUid=96&rangeStart=2740&rangeEnd=2855",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/64e325b0724ff25c64eeff7?chapterUid=96&rangeStart=2740&rangeEnd=2855"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38793820_100_596-671",
      "chapterUid": 100,
      "range": "596-671",
      "markText": "商品满足人的需要有两种方式：一是作为生活资料（即消费品）来直接满足，二是作为生产资料来间接满足。",
      "totalCount": 588,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38793820&chapterUid=100&rangeStart=596&rangeEnd=671",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/64e325b0724ff25c64eeff7?chapterUid=100&rangeStart=596&rangeEnd=671"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38793820_100_3114-3158",
      "chapterUid": 100,
      "range": "3114-3158",
      "markText": "如果一个物没有使用价值，那么其中包含的劳动也毫无用处，不能被看成是劳动，也无法形成价值。",
