      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38793820&chapterUid=100&rangeStart=3114&rangeEnd=3158",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/64e325b0724ff25c64eeff7?chapterUid=100&rangeStart=3114&rangeEnd=3158"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38793820_100_372-444",
      "chapterUid": 100,
      "range": "372-444",
      "markText": "商品是为交换而生产的对他人或社会有用的劳动产品，是使用价值和价值的统一物。就使用价值而言，不同商品有质的区别；就价值而言，不同商品只有量的差异。",
      "totalCount": 572,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38793820&chapterUid=100&rangeStart=372&rangeEnd=444",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/64e325b0724ff25c64eeff7?chapterUid=100&rangeStart=372&rangeEnd=444"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38793820_120_3827-3848",
      "chapterUid": 120,
      "range": "3827-3848",
      "markText": "计件工资是最适合资本家剥削工人的工资形式。",
